### ============================================================================
### NOTIFICATIONS — /api/v1/notifications
### ============================================================================

### List notifications (paginated)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/notifications?page=0&size=20
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}

### Get notification by ID
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/notifications/{{notificationId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}

### Create notification
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/notifications
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "title": "Travel Plan Approved",
  "message": "Your travel plan for Nigeria has been approved by Dr. Jane.",
  "type": "APPROVAL",
  "link": "/plans/1",
  "isRead": false,
  "userId": {{userId}}
}

### Update notification
PUT {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/notifications/{{notificationId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "title": "Travel Plan Approved",
  "message": "Your travel plan has been approved.",
  "isRead": true,
  "userId": {{userId}}
}

### Delete notification
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/notifications/{{notificationId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}
